data.title: Beats By Dre X JJ Lin: Music The Way The Artist Intended
data.description:
Beats Presents: JJ Lin on his experimental album “From M.E. To Myself”.

After dropping 12 studio albums over the last 10 years, JJ is ready to try something new. Watch him as he takes you on a musical journey.  Hear what he hears and feel what he feels in his new album "From M.E. To Myself."  

JJ Lin recorded this album specifically to be heard on great headphones.  Grab your Beats and truly experience this album the way the artist intended.
